{
  "texts": [
    "Predictive analytics using DL can help in predicting a patient's response to treatment and potential health risks.",
    "These models can be trained on large datasets of medical records to identify patterns and predict potential health issues.",
    "This can be particularly useful in preventive healthcare.",
    "DL models can be trained to analyze medical images such as X-rays, MRIs, and CT scans.",
    "These models can help healthcare providers identify abnormalities and diagnose diseases."
  ]
}